{"tid":137881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工人時薪28元　「中國製造」不再便宜","createTime":"2017-02-28T07:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a86f75eac72a834a2740a786118ab1c5284b9575","tid":137881,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170227/photo/bkn-20170227221859945-0227_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170227224935\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170227221859945-0227_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170227224935&h=2fe3b673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中媒引述歐睿國際(Euromonitor)最新一項調查結果指出，中國製造業員工於2016年的平均時薪為3.6美元(折合約28港元)，較2005年大增3倍，已高於除智利以外的拉丁美洲國家，更已達到歐元區中較弱成員國水平的70%左右。<br />\n<br />\n同期，巴西製造業時薪則由2.9美元降至2.7美元；墨西哥則由2.2美元降至2.1美元；南非也從4.3美元降至3.6美元。<br />\n<br />\nChina Market Research(CMR)分析師Ben Cavender接受外媒訪問時稱，由於中國工人時薪趨升，對當地製造業打擊很大，更多工廠將投資遷離中國。這意味着中國可能陸續有更多工作職位流失。<br />\n<br />\n為降低生產成本，企業或將工廠遷至其他新興市場國家，例如是斯里蘭卡。根據歐睿調查，去年斯里蘭卡製造業時薪僅為0.5美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170227/photo/bkn-20170227221859945-0227_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170227224935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170227221859945-0227_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20170227224935&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fcafd3bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170227/photo/bkn-20170227221859945-0227_00842_001_01p.jpg?20170227224935</a>"},{"pid":"d31742c5f59cf72afdb05e1d6525cfb4334676a4","tid":137881,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9547d77c4e28eb211e206ceb04f9c533f7d08fa4","tid":137881,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:31:04.000Z","