":137881,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇中國可以轉形啲咩行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起樓，起基建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已起到爛 一堆高鐵 一堆動車<br />\n<br />\n堆傻西強國人 完全唔識經濟<br />\n仲話高鐵預左蝕 事實上帶到經濟<br />\n仲係度懶經濟 up一堆咩邊際利益<br />\n<br />\n心諗<br />\n你依家人口紅利 人員流動大 就係<br />\n<br />\n未來社老人化 產業升級(唔會再有大量製造業) 使用率大減<br />\n呢堆高鐵 維修費 都隨時拖垮共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(呢個係香港高鐵的論點 一次性 費用超支反而唔係最可怕)"},{"pid":"fd7fdf2a31d1739816dc91e0f1dcc0df244e6b4c","tid":137881,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇中國可以轉形啲咩行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全民炒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地真係好井底 雖然我對支那無咩好感<br />\n但人地一早唔玩低階製衣業<br />\n你望下電子科技公司依家中國佔左幾多間先啦"},{"pid":"93643dbc0c930e83ae6d739399a93681f4ddf953","tid":137881,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經追平幾年前香港既最低時薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人民幣 &gt;&gt; 港幣<br />\n<br />\n28RMB  = 31.X 港幣"},{"pid":"0eac1ecec7f203a6d3274d3c1bf741c58ceedadd","tid":137881,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想睇中國可以轉形啲咩行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全民炒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地真係好井底 雖然我對支那無咩好感<br />\n但人地一早唔玩低階製衣業<br />\n你望下電子科技公司依家中國佔左幾多間先啦</blockquote><br />\n電子科技.....仲係以價錢低作賣點<br />\n真係做到日韓咁賣質素先算啦"},{"pid":"149fc3a27caeac1394fa5ddca954a2593ff7b872","tid":137881,"ui